{
  "stem": "6719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a friend whose father was an engineer, and who told me that when he grows up-- I think he was 12 years old or 13 years old-- that he's going to go to the [NON-ENGLISH] to become an engineer in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I wanted to become an engineer, but it didn't-- it had no meaning whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd say so, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, first of all, nobody talked to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was persona non grata, uh, with the exception of-- I do recall this-- this-- this Rudy Kamfierer who went to school with me, uh, uh, who-- who was, uh, known to be an-- an illegal Nazi, as they called him, because the Nazi party wasn't allowed to exist, uh, between 1933 and-- 1934 and 1938.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The government disallowed all the parties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just one party.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, used to wear those white stockings and-- and the leiderhosen, you know, the leather pants.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that always, uh, uh, showed people who was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was Rudy Kamfierer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rudy Kamfierer used to go with me-- I remember that incident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Uh, in our building, in our house, you know, there was-- there were a couple of businesses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a dry cleaning and there was a-- a green grocer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the green grocer was-- I-- I can only say right now was a nebbish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Uh, he-- he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He wasn't stupid or something like that, but he had-- he was always walking bent forward, and he was very frail.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we, as kids, used to make fun of him, everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
